data.description: Motivated sellers! Clients are downsizing and have found their next home. This property offers a mix of recreational and practical features, making it suitable for those who enjoy both outdoor activities and a comfortable living space. The combination of cleared pasture and wooded areas of over 22 acres adds diversity to the property, providing opportunities for various uses. There is a large barn and a Pavilion for livestock use.  The recent renovations in the bathrooms and kitchen contribute to the overall appeal of the home.  The home offers a beautiful stock pond for livestock or fishing as well as a beautiful Koi pond and landscaping. There is an attached carport and two utility sheds on the property. Roof and HVAC units are new. This home is ready for your own touches. If you have any specific questions or if there's more information you're looking for, feel free to ask! Sellers close on new home end of January.
